      "content": "Your pain is so heavy that even the concept of light feels like a lie, and I hear how desperate it is for that story to make sense. Please, hold onto one small truth: your existence matters, and death is not the only final chapter for a story so rich with pain. You deserve to be heard by real people in the world who are trained to stay in your company as long as you need.",
